  <summary date="2017-03-08T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">American Law Enforcement Heroes Act of 2017

This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to include as an allowable use of grant funds under the Community Oriented Policing Services program prioritizing the hiring and training of veterans as career law enforcement officers.</summary>
